</head><body><table border=0 align=center width=80%><tr><td class=textbody><center><h1>BrainBite (Ryla Bottle)</h1><br>by Aelina of Cazic Thule</center><br><table width="573" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="center">

  <tr> 

    <td>

      <div align="center"><b>Getting the Ryla Bottle from Karnor's Castle with 

        a Low Level Rogue<br>

        </b
      </div>

    </td>

  </tr>

  <tr> 

    <td>

      <hr noshade width="250">

    </td>

  </tr>

  <tr> 

    <td height="531"> 

      <p>Get a rogue to either Firiona Vie or The overthere. Get the rogue bound 

        at that location. Best to have some SOW potions in the bank. Drink an 

        SOW potion and have another on hand incase the first runs out. Hide and 

        Sneak on all the way to Karnors. Do a quick /ooc or /shout to find out 

        if the human skeleton is up on anyone's tracking. Once moving into Karnor's 

        don't stop for anything. Hide and Sneak on, head straight accross the bridge 

        and through the gate area. Turn left and then go up the stairs that will 

        shortly be on the right. At the top of the stairs go left. When you get 

        to the outside of the wall turn right and go all the way to the end. At 

        that point your only option will be to turn right. (I can't remember from 

        there the written directions to the jail, you just need to get to the 

        jail). Go to the second cell on the right. Open the door and go in. Go 

        to the corner as far from the door as possible. Note: from here you must 

        not be in full screen mode, time is very precious and you can not afford 

        even the miniscule delay of the screen switching modes for the trade window. 

        Turn so that the skel is on the left side of the screen, again to save 

        time moving the cursor to the give button. Pick up the jar from your inventory 

        and move it over the skel. Now double click. Two clicks are needed because 

        the first does nothing but kill your hide and sneak. Quickly move the 

        cursor to the give button and click. Right about then the Drolvarg in 

        the cell across the hall will kill you. After you pop back up at your 

        bind point get an SOW potion or two from the bank and get back to Karnors 

        the same way you went the first time. Once inside, follow the same path 

        to the jail, again hiding and sneaking. Even if you can see your corpse 

        through the wall you have to get to right in front of the door to start 

        draging it. Drag your corpse to the zone and loot it. Viola! One bottle 

        of swirling smoke. </p>

      <p>Note: very infrequently one of the little drolvargs in Karnors will see 

        you while hiding and sneaking and you will die an extra time. Don't sweat 

        it and don't run for the zone, even if you make it your just going to 

        piss off several people by training a bunch of mobs to the zone line. 

        Just make the slow run again. </p>

      <p>This was done with a level 8 rogue, but level 6 is all that's really needed 

        to make sure the corpse lasts long enough though, I reccommend at least 

        level 7 to make sure you don't drop to 5 in the process. </p>

      <p>Oh and if anyone on the Cazic Thule server wants me to get this one for 

        them with my rogue at the overthere I'll gladly do it. For an exorbatant 

        price of course ;) </p>

      <p>Aelina <br>

        Wizard of Neriak </p>

    </td>

  </tr>

