    <td>

      <p><i>Note from Graffe-</p>

      <p>For those who are asking, "Great. I've got a bottle on a level 7 

        rogue. Now what do I do with it?" There is a trick that works with 

        all quests. Anyone can turn in any number of items that are required for 

        a quest, but to get the finished quest item, the person that wants to 

        receive it must be the last person to hit 'GIVE'.</i></p>

    </td>

  </tr>

